>https://imgur.com/a/TYJIB5i</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[fulcrims]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Well, that hit me harder than expected...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IiTynHg</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EmLaUpL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>First, HUGE TLDR warning. So, watching Encanto with my girlfriend and this wonderful character pops up. We've all heard of her, Luisa. But I never thought how much I'd connect to this character and, this song. Mind, I'm a dude and not even the oldest but... Listening to it, I just kinda sat in shock, and felt every time I had to carry my family, how I had to be the strongest if someone needed help moving, fixing something.... and beyond that, the strongest when something happens and peace needs to be made, the strongest when someone calls crying... and I feel her, but more, I feel time. Then at work I'm always on call. I spend 70% of my time helping others, pushing to make the place I work the happiest and most productive place possible. Washing floors, moving plants, furniture, fucking carpentry if needed, in addition to books, managing funds, tenants and even there I try to listen, help when I can. But I'm so tired of carrying... everything. Physically, emotionally... just tired. 

Anyway, I'm watching it and my girlfriend says my mouth is just open. She thought I was just getting lost in movies like I do from time to time, but at the end, when this hug happened, something broke and I just cried.... Not holding back tears, just lost it totally. My love paused it, hugged me and now... I think I need to have a talk with my family, and with my friends at work. So I'm doing something the woman who loves me showed, write it out, but instead of burning the thoughts, I am leaving them here.

Here's to you Luisa, and here's to all the sisters and brothers who carry everything. May your back stay strong. 

I'll try watching it again tomorrow. Right now I just need a nap. Lovey, if you come across this, I love you so much, and wouldn't be strong without you.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IiTynHg</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Illpostcheese]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>the left hand doesn't know what the right hand is doing</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qUlnlqs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xqBRKxT.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qUlnlqs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[upvoteHero]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>&quot;I've only known this Halfling for a day... but if anything happened to her, I'd kill everyone in this forest and then myself.&quot;</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wzBf8Oc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XZCFUSj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Art by Saint Monster - https://twitter.com/saintmonstre</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CUqgY86.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1lIFmkJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AOhzcYC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wzBf8Oc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Pasquinel]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Yep</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vUvUz8X</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JXowXqv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Deserves a reposting...</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vUvUz8X</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ivonator]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It is my cake day.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mn